            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "An irradiation head with three targets in series was",
                "used, which allowed the simultaneous irradiation of",
                "U-238+O(2), Al-27 and Th-232+O(2), as the proton beam",
                "was not affected significantly by the targets",
                "themselves. Each actinide target consisted of approx.",
                " 240 mg of microspheres, approx. 0.3 mm in diameter."
              ]
